\f1\b 4. LLM-as-Judge \'97 Istara Already Has It
\f0\b0 \
\
    
\f1\b What Istara has:
\f0\b0 \
     - core/validation.py: 
\f1\b Adversarial Review
\f0\b0  (one model critiques another), 
\f1\b Dual-Run
\f0\b0  (two models compare), 
\f1\b Full Ensemble
\f0\b0  (3+ models\
