\f4\b\fs26 \cf0 \strokec2 AgentScope is the better framework
\f3\b0 \strokec2 \'a0for developers who want to build custom agent applications. It has better voice support, training capabilities, formal evaluation, and deployment flexibility.\

\f4\b \strokec2 Istara is the better product
\f3\b0 \strokec2 \'a0for UX researchers who need a complete, secure, self-improving research platform. It has domain expertise, evidence chains, security, and a full UI that AgentScope simply doesn\'92t provide.\

